). Capsule (
Figs 12–14
): Juxta and vinculum strongly fused with valvae, vinculum weakly fused with tegumen, vinculum arms laterally expanded and weakly fused midventrally, diaphragma membranous except for juxta/anellus. Valvae (
Figs 15
